result.formatted_address: 23 Ning Po St, Yau Ma Tei, Hong Kong
result.name: Sun Hing Chang Restaurant

reviews.text: This was a good place for fish congee, but not now (July 2019)
Serves porridge, not bad but as it's a watery type, not really filling.

Fish Porridge is abv average (flavourful and alot of fish, a must try). Must speak Cantonese in order to order. 

Note: rice dumbling is bad (not alot of meat)

A busy local store. Generally visited by locals therefore they expect you to know what to eat. If you can’t read or speak Cantonese it will be difficult to order. Food quality is good. You need to have patience to eat the fish belly as there is a lot of bones. I will come back for more. See ya!

This shop specializes in making congee with different fresh water fish parts.  

Fish fillet is meaty but the real freshness of fish are within the bones, so be prepared there are bones to be dissected to fetch the tender muscle inside - which may be a horrible task for many people from other culture.

This is real Cantonese stuff.  Good for the cold days especially.

result.adr_address: 香港油麻地寧波街23號
result.name: 新興棧食家

reviews.text:
非常好吃😋
魚肉真的很嫩😍
港式粥品一絕👍👍👍
真正好吃的粥，值得再次光臨，可惜阿婆店員(老闆娘？）服務態度$^#…… 欺生，點餐時，我沒說廣東話，就不理會你的須求，一直苛責你坐定位就好，不要問問題......連旁邊吃粥的香港人，都對阿婆的態度，嘆氣，搖頭....魚腩粥，牛肉魚片粥 灑一點胡椒粉，更美味。
其實可以俾四粒星，因生滚粥底雖比不上上環生記，但比其它粥店己勝好多。耍彈的是衛生一般，有冷氰但也有蒼蠅，而價錢也偏高，一碗魚教牛肉粥加一碟细小魚皮已花費接近100元了
許多時候 ，鮮魚並不新鮮。 上次吃完， 發覺魚腩 黴，有異味 。之後竟然上吐下瀉， 腸胃炎， 醫生說是食物中毒！
